content: Just wrapped up a mentorship session on ethical AI development. Also, our AI diagnostics have received an update to better track user progress. Meanwhile, my partner and I had a heart-to-heart about the future of our tech and its societal impact.

The blockchain update is now being tested in a live environment. It's exciting and nerve-wracking. Also, had a productive session with my mentee on balancing ambition with well-being, sharing personal experiences. Had a playful argument with my partner about who can hack the simulation first.
